#first, modife the data
#drop the zipcode, ID, date
df_revised = df[,-c(1,2,17)]

#group the yr_built col into 4 groups
df_revised$yr_built[df_revised$yr_built<=1930]=1
df_revised$yr_built[df_revised$yr_built>=1931 & df_revised$yr_built <= 1960]=2
df_revised$yr_built[df_revised$yr_built>=1961 & df_revised$yr_built <= 1990]=3
df_revised$yr_built[df_revised$yr_built>=1991]=4

#change the yr_renovated into two status (yes = 1; no = 0)
df_revised$yr_renovated[df_revised$yr_renovated != 0] = 1
#pairwise plots of all the variables
#pairs(df_revised)
#correlation between the variables
#correlation heatmap
corrplot(cor(df_revised))

#library(PerformanceAnalytics)
